{"tid":473201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美租車公司把西藏、新疆、台灣及南海從支那地圖剔除","createTime":"2017-11-19T04:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T04:13:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98917e64def6b2c301ee870374cb1c68493b094a","tid":473201,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171119/large/1511063883_aeec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171119%2Flarge%2F1511063883_aeec.jpg&h=d105c438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近，支那微博網友「魚kipedia」發現，國際知名租車品牌「企業租車」(Enterprise Rent-A-Car)直接將西藏、新疆、台灣及南海從支那地圖中剔除，將支那地圖變得「面目全非」。<br />\n<br />\n有關事件在支那共青團中央官方微博貼出後，即時引起網民激烈反應，有人要求永久禁止與其合作，也有人提出決不使用。據公開資料，「企業租車」運營至今已超過50年，而該公司網頁更與支那一嗨租車有聯繫。而今日有關網頁上的支那地圖已被更改。"},{"pid":"5171332ea6ea056eac5b2c35bf5ca0dff3f55a63","tid":473201,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/m36li8al1/MAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2Fm36li8al1%2FMAP.jpg&h=c91a8396&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce61dd7871b0e60569cf21ffe1be950f3c8c759","tid":473201,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"美國租車差不多次次都用 enterprise <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a257c0d5c1dfb9847fcf9fe198625c6f018f0c","tid":473201,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZ